                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#31rb">f. 31rb</locus>
                           <desc>(below): gʷǝlt-charter (continuation of Additio 1). </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#31rb">31rb</locus>: ወጕልተ፡ ዘጐለቱ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ደቂቁ፡ ለገብረ፡ አምላክ፡
